file: tmp_【#SSholoX】世界征服に向けて…【3Dアジトお披露目】 [aGp1Q3aH_Bk]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_007.mov

scenes.description: The members of holoX prepare for Chloe's turn in the 'Secret Silhouette' game.
Sakamata Chloe attempts her silhouette challenge but fails and is launched into the air.
The group discusses Iroha's previous easy success and prepares her for a second attempt.
Kazama Iroha faces a sword-shaped silhouette challenge, but despite her efforts, she fails and is launched.
The members tease the leader, La+ Darknesss, before her turn, and she vows to take on everyone's feelings.
La+ Darknesss attempts a seemingly easy silhouette but gets launched anyway.
Feeling the game is unfair, Lui and La+ decide to try a dual challenge together.
Lui and La+ attempt the dual silhouette challenge and both are launched into the air.
The whole group decides to perform a final challenge together, practicing their poses.
All five members try to match a 'holoX' logo silhouette but fail and are all launched at once.
